title: I would find her society much more believable if it was set far in the future on some other planet, and did not require the reader to swallow a total reversal of current trends.

Uncommon Women (1983)
The only problem I had with the movie was that it fails to develop its material.

A shallow cash-grab.
More troubling is the is the lecturing on the evils of capitalism and how it was responsible for all the ecological troubles of the world.
